title: Ernie Haase Discography 1995-2012 (30 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
ERNIE HAASE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 30 releases...

 * 1995 - Amen
 * 1995 - Journey On
 * 1999 - What A Difference A Day Makes
 * 2000 - Never Alone
 * 2002 - Building A Bridge
 * 2002 - Building A Bridge - Playback
 * 2002 - Celebration Time
 * 2002 - Stand By Me
 * 2002 - Stand By Me - Playback
 * 2003 - Glory To His Name
 * 2003 - Glory To His Name - Playback
 * 2004 - Christmas With Ernie Haase And Signature Sound
 * 2004 - Christmas With Ernie Haase And Signature Sound - Playback
 * 2004 - Great Love
 * 2004 - Stand By Me Live
 * 2004 - The Ground Is Level
 * 2004 - The Ground Is Level - Playback
 * 2005 - Ernie Haase
 * 2005 - Great Love - Playback
 * 2006 - Get Away, Jordan
 * 2006 - Get Away, Jordan - Playback
 * 2007 - Together
 * 2008 - Dream On
 * 2008 - Influenced
 * 2009 - Every Light That Shines At Christmas
 * 2010 - A Tribute To The Cathedrals Quartet
 * 2010 - Influenced Spirituals And Southern Classics
 * 2011 - A White Christmas
 * 2012 - California Live, Vol 1
 * 2012 - Here We Are Again

Ernie Haase is an American singer. He is best known as the former tenor singer of the Southern gospel group The Cathedrals. After the Cathedrals' retirement, Haase became the founder of Ernie Haase and Signature Sound.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
